Date:   Wed May 20 02:04:52 2026 -0400

    Add OpenAPI 3.0.3 spec generation and Swagger UI

    - New src/openapi.ts module: generates OpenAPI spec dynamically from
      API_CATALOGS for all enabled services, and renders Swagger UI HTML
    - New GET /openapi.json endpoint: returns the live OpenAPI spec as JSON,
      scoped to currently configured services
    - New GET /docs endpoint: serves interactive Swagger UI pointing at /openapi.json
    - Both endpoints are public (no auth required) to support tool discovery
    - Zero TypeScript errors; all 63 existing tests pass

